Title: Connection of my dear country to world
DateModified: '2019-02-15'
DatePublished: '2019-02-15'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/connection-of-my-dear-country-to-world
SetInCountry: Afghanistan
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Hura Naeemi
AuthorCountry: Afghanistan
Text: 'I want to introduce my lovely country to world. The my great wish is that ,which  connect
  all country with other.l will journey the European countries , so I want know the
  culture of Portugal s people I want see the level education, secure , economy, and
  I want know the type of it is life style , situation of women life, condition of
  the children, condition of its school and higher education . Most important from
  all of them I want know the healthcare progression because I am a doctor and my
  great goal is that , which irradicate diseases in the world I want  be healthy all
  people in the world. I am sure this day will be close. I am a girl so I want play
  a key role in the name of an Afghan s girl as a young person ,doctor , educated
  person , and also as a young leader. By this travel I will know that how the Portugal
  country and other European countries Improve their  higher education , health situation,
  nutrition , security , economy , culture , food , healthcare services.....

  I want see the rivers , ocean .. and also the type of clothing , eating food , it''s
  meals , fruit  . And also the treatment of their people.'
